        <description>
          &lt;img src=&quot;https://dalton.newbend.art/shows/parker-house-rolls-cafe/1_hu_d074d373ccf23802.jpg&quot; /&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;An experiment embarks in parker house rolls cafe where viewers step into the thoughts and process of a young homemaker and prose writer who worships nostalgia and material. See through their eyes the wonders of bric-a-brac, tools, and furniture. Where the lines between precious and worthless are forgotten, and company is always welcome.&lt;/p&gt;
        </description></item>
